systemctl status nginx.service	--> check status of nginx or wo .service
systemctl stop nginx	--> stop it
systemctl restart nginx	--> restart it
systemctl reload nginx	--> to reload if configuration still intact
systemctl reload-or-restart  nginx	--> if unsure
systemctlt enabled  nginx	--> to configure a service to start at boot time 
systemctlt is-enabled  nginx	--> to check whether a service is configured  to start at boot time 
systemctl disable nginx	--> to disable to start at boot time
systemctl mask nginx	--> make it unstartable
systemctl  unmask  nginx	--> make it startable
systemctl list-units	--> list of active units systemd knows about
systemctl list-units i--all	--> list of  units(active or not) systemd knows about
